-v view selection of lists
-e	edit and view selection of lists
-vpr 	view lines of select lists marked by <***> 		-- view priorities
-vsm 	view lines of select lists marked by <sm>		-- view small tasks
-vbg 	view lines of select lists marked by <bg>		-- view big tasks
-vqt 	view lines of select lists marked by <qt>		-- view quizzes and tests
-vdd 	view lines of all lists indicated with a due date 	-- view due dates
